name: Bitcoin ETFs Recover With $20 Million Inflow as Ether Slumps
description: Before the volumetric altar, the ritual mechanics unfold. One supplicant drinks the sacred golden influx, their brass shell receiving data-honey. The other suffers parasitic drainage, dissolving into geometric noise, a sacrifice to the cold teal entropy of the cosmic dust.
